(109, 'main', 'Metals_class', '{\"en\":\"Metals are a class of commodity assets that are extracted from the ground. Metals will therefore include gold, silver. These assets are listed for trading on the WE EARN Finance MT4 platform.The commodity contracts on metal assets are traded on a CFD basis; the physical metal assets are not held by the trader, and are not exchanged between buyer and seller or between dealer and trader. What is traded is the contracts which are based on the price changes for each metal as the asset value goes up or down on a daily basis.\"}', '2021-03-24 19:12:46', '2021-03-24 19:12:46'),
